title: Hair Regrow 7 Day, Ginger Germinal Essential Oil Hair Growth Hair Loss Treatment Hair Care Hair Growth Serum for Men & Women, 30ml
description:
About products:-

MILD FORMULA-No smell, No skin sting. Do not affect your daily life. No sense of itch. Organic Hair Growth Serum - Stimulates & Nourishes Hair Follicles & Scalp. Designed To Revitalize, Strengthen And Protect. For Hair Restoration, Stronger, Thicker & Long Lasting Hair.


SUGGESTED USE-For the best results, mix 2 - 3 drops of the hair growth essential oil with shampoo. Work a quarter-sized amount of product into palms and massage into your scalp, working from root to tip of hair using your fingertips. Wash your hair thoroughly with warm water. You can also use another method of use: Mix it With Shampoo For Use. Please inject 3 ml hair growth oil into each 100ml shampoo and stir it evenly for use.
